    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、使えそうな小道具は水鉄砲と浮き輪……\nならあのポーズが……こう、かしら？",
      "startTime": 23.5333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、あのグラビア雑誌で見たポーズが活かせそうね\nこんな感じでもっと儚さを……うーん……",
      "startTime": 33.2333325068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　沙季だけ一人でずっと歩き回ったり\n唸ったりしているが……まさか調子が悪いのか？",
      "startTime": 42.5999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……すみません、ご心配をお掛けしました\nですが、調子は悪いどころか、良過ぎるぐらいです",
      "startTime": 51.5333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "本当か？　九月に入ったとはいえまだ日差しも強い\n熱中症だったら大変だぞ、無理はしないでくれよ",
      "startTime": 60.599999237,
      "sfxList": []
    }
